Happy New Year! We ve been working hard on new features and improvements and are excited to bring you the following in our 4.3 update: iPhone 6s and 6s Plus users can take advantage of the hardware s 3D touch feature. Press and hold on the app icon to quickly jump to various shortcuts including resuming the last movie you were watching! In the app you can press and hold to get a Peek at a movie and press harder to Pop and start playback. You can also press and hold on a category to get a Peek at the contents within that category and press harder to Pop the category in to view. Enhanced the app launch user experience. Improved in app sign up process. Various bug fixes. And from our previous updates: Search for movies to watch right from Spotlight search. Type in a movie or actor s name and results from Feeln will show right in Spotlight! If you have a Chromecast device streaming is an easy tap away! If you encounter any issues please contact us at support feeln.com and we will gladly help you out.
